title: Vega
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Music venue by night, a restaurant by day, this place is located in the Railyard section of the Haymarket. The Railyard has a giant outdoor video screen with lots of outdoor seating and it's a to hang out. The menu is  burgers and "haute" dogs with a unique offering of toppings, sauces, and sides. Offers a veggie burger, a carrot dog, and a shangri la salad with fried tofu. Full bar with draft beer.
